song.title: Capital Kings - I Feel So Alive (eXOdus Remix)
song.info:
My remix of the song "I Feel So Alive" by Capital Kings. Made using Renoise. All sounds except for drums were made/resampled using the Image Line Harmor VSTi.
Soundcloud link: https://soundcloud.com/exodus-6/capital-kings-i-feel-so-alive
